# https://w3id.org/dbc-ontology/ redirects via HTTP 303 using content negotiation:
# - HTML requests are redirected to:
#   https://paitools.github.io/DBCOntology/documentation/index-en.html
# - RDF/OWL requests are redirected to:
#   https://paitools.github.io/DBCOntology/DBC.owl

